cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI, cs.IT. 

The paper deals with online clustering of bandits, which is a problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a more efficient algorithm using set structures, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses regret bounds, which is a topic in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
